description: A rare excavation south of Oslo will provide new details about Viking culture.
title: Norway excavates a Viking longship fit for a king
title_page: Norway excavates a Viking longship fit for a king - BBC News
maintext: "On the coast it's hard to use a sail, the wind changes all the time, so you would often row a ship. But to cross, say, from Bergen to Shetland it was better to wait for the right wind."
